  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Effect of High-flow nasal cannula oxygen on end-expiratory lung volumes determined by
      electrical impedance tomography
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Prospective clinical study in ICU with patients requiring High-flow nasal cannula oxygen
      comparing lung volumes determined by electrical impedance tomography and diaphragmatic
      ultrasound before, during and after High-flow nasal cannula oxygen.

      Duration of High-flow nasal cannula oxygen is 30 minutes.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
